The result I'm trying to get, as a css class, this:
.dnd_areahome-row-2-background-gradient {
     background-image: linear-gradient (to right, rgba (203, 214, 226, 1) 0%, rgba (203, 214, 226, 1) 70%, rgba (255, 255, 255, 1) 70%) ! important;
}
